## üìö Overview
The **Marketing** category connects n8n workflows with modern **content creation, automation, CRM, and analytics tools**.  
From **email campaigns** and **social media automation** to **SEO**, **video marketing**, and **AI-powered content creation**, these integrations allow marketers to streamline lead generation, engagement, and reporting ‚Äî all in one place.

